and is a  honors college graduate of michigan state university in  while at harvard law school abraham helped found the harvard journal of law and public policy it became one of the official journals of the federalist society which was founded in  political careeredit before his election to the senate abraham was a law professor at thomas m cooley law school republican party serviceedit he was elected chairman of the michigan republican party from  to  he was deputy chief of staff for vice president dan quayle from  to  he later served as cochairman of the national republican congressional committee nrcc from  to  and ran for chairman of the republican national committee in  coming second to haley barbour united states senateedit abraham was elected to represent michigan in the united states senate in  and he served until  when he was defeated for reelection to the senate in  for a second term by debbie stabenow he was the only arab american in the chamber according to the new york times state republicans attributed his loss to scathing advertisements by a wide range of special interest groups including advertisements that criticized mr abrahams support for a relaxation of some immigration restrictions during the campaign the federation for american immigration reform ran ads asking why is senator spencer abraham trying to make it easier for terrorists like osama bin laden to export their war of terror to any city street in america the media denounced these commercials as vengeful in  when president clinton endorsed congresswoman barbara jordans proposed cuts to legal immigration senator abraham played a leading role in blocking the proposed cuts another factor in his defeat was his vote to convict president clinton in his  impeachment trial the following year he received the defender of the melting pot award from the national council of la raza for his efforts on the immigration issue this section possibly contains original research please improve it by verifying the claims made and adding inline citations statements consisting only of original research should be removed october  learn how and when to remove this template message committee service and legislationedit he served on the budget commerce science and transportation judiciary and small business committees he also chaired two subcommittees manufacturing and competitiveness and immigration abraham authored the hb visa in global and national commerce act establishing a federal framework for online contracts and signatures the government paperwork elimination act and the anticybersquatting consumer protection act which protects internet domain names for businesses and persons against copyright and trademark infringements in  abraham cosponsored s a bill to abolish the us department of energy which would have transferred control of the strategic petroleum reserve in large part to the defense department us energy secretaryedit spencer abraham working as the secretary of energy near yucca mountain abraham was appointed secretary of energy by the incoming george w bushs administration on november   abraham announced that he would resign from this position effective with the swearing in of his successor samuel w bodman on february   in  lebanese ambassador farid abboud awarded abraham the national order of the cedar hoover institutionedit abraham was a distinguished visiting fellow at the hoover institution an influential think tank based at stanford university from  through  after leaving office abraham opened the abraham group a washington dc based international strategic consulting firm in  spencer abraham accepted the appointment as chairman of the board of areva inc the us subsidiary of the french nuclear energy company thompson for presidentedit on july   abraham was announced as an ambassador to official washington in the fred thompson presidential campaign later careeredit in  abraham was appointed nonexecutive chairman of the board of areva inc the american arm of the french nuclear company areva which is planning to build epr nuclear power plants in the united states and is building the mixed oxide fuel mox manufacturing plant at the savannah river site to convert legacy weaponsgrade plutonium into power station fuel with william tucker abraham wrote lights out ten myths about and real solutions to americas energy crisis which was published in july  abraham is also the chairman and ceo of the abraham group a strategic consulting firm providing assistance to clients seeking opportunities in the us and global markets electoral historyedit michigan us senate election  party candidate votes  ± democratic debbie stabenow   republican spencer abraham incumbent   michigan us senate election  party candidate votes  ± republican spencer abraham   democratic bob carr   libertarian jon coon   referencesedit  httppoliticalgraveyardcomgroupeasternorthodoxhtml  harvard journal of law and public policy archived from the original on  retrieved    the  elections michigan congresswoman unseats a senator the new york times november   retrieved july     archived copy archived from the original on  retrieved    archived copy archived from the original on  retrieved    httpwwwfairusorgsitepageserver  article dead link  pear robert june   clinton embraces a proposal to cut immigration by a third the new york times   httpwwwwashingtonpostcomwpsrvpoliticsspecialclintonstoriesgophtm  krikorian mark august   liberal twostep dems pay lip service only on border control national review   httpthomaslocgovcgibinbdqueryzdsnlsummm  farid abboud awards spencer abraham the national order of the cedar archived from the original on  retrieved    spencer abraham nommé président du conseil d’administration d’areva inc in french framatome anp march     the politico f thompson shakes up prelaunch campaign by jonathan martin and mike allen july    jo becker and william j broad april   new doubts about turning plutonium into a fuel new york times retrieved april     a 