 sir bernard burke  does not list that couple as having any child named abraham although it does list their other children page  abraham spencer b  yorkshire england m scrivener judith  thomas spencer  george spencer  john spencer  william spencer  john spencer  d dec  martins hundred james city virginia usa httpwwwwittmeyerfamilycomthomasspencerhtml view all abraham spencers timeline   birth of abraham yorkshire england  december   age  birth of thomas spencer i james city virginia   age  birth of john spencer virginia   age  birth of john spencer sheffield yorkshire england  december   age  death of abraham martins hundred james city virginia genealogy directory a b c d e f g h i j k l m n o p q r s t u v w x y z app   genicomaboutdirectorysurnametermsprivacyblogwikiworld family treehelp follow usbe a fan english us   eesti   svenska   español españa   français   עברית   norsk bokmål   dansk   nederlands   deutsch   » abraham spencer worldcat identities abraham spencer overview works  works in  publications in  languages and  library holdings genres television news programs  nonfiction television programs  televised speeches  radio speeches  nonfiction radio programs  roles author speaker interviewee classifications jv  publication timeline  most widely held works about spencer abraham spencer abraham nomination  hearing before the committee on energy and natural resources united states senate one hundred seventh congress first session nominee to be secretary of the department of energy january   by united states book  spencer abraham     abraham spencer  thank goodness for bush  i cant wait to get rid of that washington insiders crowd by herbert block visual  abraham spencer by sir john harvey by nell marion nugent  the thomas m cooley law school and oakland university cordially invite you to attend energy security presented by former secretary of energy spencer abraham  monday october    pm meadow brook theatre oakland university book    more fewer most widely h